{
  "meta": {
    "is_partial": true,
    "description": "게시글 상세 본문 (basic 유형). 게시글 본문 카드 + 댓글 권한 안내 + 댓글 섹션 + 답글 섹션"
  },
  "comment": "게시글 상세 (본문 카드 + 댓글 + 답글)",
  "type": "basic",
  "name": "Div",
  "blur_until_loaded": {
    "enabled": true,
    "data_sources": "post"
  },
  "children": [
    {
      "comment": "게시글 본문 카드",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "card bg-base-100 shadow-sm"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "comment": "게시글 헤더 (제목, 배지, 작성자, 조회수)",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": {
            "className": "p-6 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "comment": "1줄: 배지 + 제목 + NEW (순서: 비밀글 아이콘 > 카테고리 > 공지 | 제목 NEW)",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "props": {
                "className": "mb-3 flex items-center flex-wrap"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "comment": "배지 그룹 (비밀글 아이콘 > 카테고리 > 공지) - 배지가 있을 때만 표시",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "if": "{{post?.data?.category || post?.data?.is_notice || post?.data?.is_secret || post?.data?.status === 'blinded'}}",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "flex items-center gap-3 flex-shrink-0 mr-3"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "comment": "공지 배지",
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{post?.data?.is_notice}}",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "px-2 py-1 text-xs font-bold bg-blue-600 text-white dark:bg-blue-500 rounded"
                      },
                      "text": "$t:board.notice"
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "카테고리 배지",
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{post?.data?.category}}",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 rounded"
                      },
                      "text": "{{post.data.category}}"
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "비밀글 아이콘",
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "Icon",
                      "if": "{{post?.data?.is_secret}}",
                      "props": {
                        "name": "lock",
                        "size": "sm",
                        "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "블라인드 아이콘",
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "Icon",
                      "if": "{{post?.data?.status === 'blinded'}}",
                      "props": {
                        "name": "eye-slash",
                        "size": "sm",
                        "className": "text-orange-500 dark:text-orange-400 flex-shrink-0"
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "comment": "제목 + NEW 배지 (붙여서 표시)",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "flex items-center gap-2 flex-1 min-w-0"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "comment": "제목",
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "H1",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
                      },
                      "text": "{{post?.data?.title ?? ''}}"
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "삭제됨 배지",
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{post?.data?.deleted_at}}",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-red-100 text-red-700 dark:bg-red-900/30 dark:text-red-300 flex-shrink-0"
                      },
                      "text": "$t:board.post.deleted_badge"
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "새글 배지 (제목 바로 옆)",
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{post?.data?.is_new}}",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "px-2 py-1 text-xs font-bold bg-red-500 text-white rounded flex-shrink-0"
                      },
                      "text": "N"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "작성자 정보 + 조회수/댓글수",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "props": {
                "className": "flex items-center justify-between"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "comment": "작성자 정보",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "flex items-center gap-3"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "Avatar",
                      "props": {
                        "author": "{{post?.data?.author}}",
                        "size": "md"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "UserInfo",
                      "props": {
                        "author": "{{post?.data?.author}}"
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "comment": "날짜/조회수/댓글수",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "comment": "작성일",
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "props": {
                        "title": "{{post?.data?.created_at ?? ''}}"
                      },
                      "text": "{{post?.data?.created_at_formatted ?? ''}}"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{post?.data?.board?.show_view_count !== false && post?.data?.view_count !== undefined}}",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "flex items-center gap-1"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "composite",
                          "name": "Icon",
                          "props": {
                            "name": "eye",
                            "size": "sm"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Span",
                          "text": "{{post.data.view_count}}"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{post?.data?.board?.use_comment && post?.data?.comment_count !== undefined}}",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "flex items-center gap-1"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "composite",
                          "name": "Icon",
                          "props": {
                            "name": "message-square",
                            "size": "sm"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Span",
                          "text": "{{post.data.comment_count}}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "첨부파일 (정상 조회 가능한 경우)",
          "if": "{{post?.data?.status !== 'blinded' && post?.data?.content !== null}}",
          "partial": "partials/board/show/_post_attachments.json"
        },
        {
          "comment": "원글 정보 (답글인 경우에만 표시) - 인용 스타일",
          "if": "{{post?.data?.parent}}",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": {
            "className": "mx-6 mt-4 p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700/50 border-l-4 border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 rounded-r-lg"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "comment": "1줄: 원글 아이콘 + 라벨 (왼쪽) / 작성자 + 날짜 (오른쪽)",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "props": {
                "className": "flex items-center justify-between mb-2 text-sm"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "comment": "왼쪽: 아이콘 + 라벨",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "flex items-center gap-2"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "Icon",
                      "props": {
                        "name": "message-square",
                        "size": "sm",
                        "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                      },
                      "text": "$t:board.parent_post"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "comment": "오른쪽: 작성자 + 날짜",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "flex items-center gap-2"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                      },
                      "text": "{{post?.data?.parent?.author?.name ?? ''}}"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500",
                        "title": "{{post?.data?.parent?.created_at ?? ''}}"
                      },
                      "text": "{{post?.data?.parent?.created_at_formatted ?? ''}}"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "2줄: 제목 (클릭 시 원글로 이동)",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "props": {
                "className": "flex items-center gap-2 mb-2"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "comment": "비밀글 아이콘",
                  "if": "{{post?.data?.parent?.is_secret}}",
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "lock",
                    "size": "sm",
                    "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "comment": "카테고리 배지",
                  "if": "{{post?.data?.parent?.category}}",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "px-2 py-0.5 text-xs rounded bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                  },
                  "text": "{{post?.data?.parent?.category ?? ''}}"
                },
                {
                  "comment": "제목 (클릭 가능, 굵게)",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "A",
                  "props": {
                    "href": "/board/{{route.slug}}/{{post?.data?.parent?.id ?? ''}}",
                    "className": "font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"
                  },
                  "text": "{{post?.data?.parent?.title ?? ''}}"
                },
                {
                  "comment": "삭제됨 배지",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "if": "{{post?.data?.parent?.deleted_at}}",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-red-100 text-red-700 dark:bg-red-900/30 dark:text-red-300 flex-shrink-0"
                  },
                  "text": "$t:board.post.deleted_badge"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "3줄: 내용 (토글로 접기/펼치기)",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "props": {
                "className": "text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3 {{_local?.parentContentExpanded ? '' : 'line-clamp-2'}}"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "comment": "블라인드 처리된 경우",
                  "if": "{{post?.data?.parent?.status === 'blinded'}}",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "italic text-orange-500 dark:text-orange-400"
                  },
                  "text": "$t:board.blinded_post"
                },
                {
                  "comment": "비밀글인 경우",
                  "if": "{{post?.data?.parent?.status !== 'blinded' && post?.data?.parent?.is_secret && post?.data?.parent?.content === null}}",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 italic"
                  },
                  "text": "$t:board.posts.detail.reply_secret_content"
                },
                {
                  "comment": "일반 글인 경우 - 내용",
                  "if": "{{post?.data?.parent?.status !== 'blinded' && !(post?.data?.parent?.is_secret && post?.data?.parent?.content === null)}}",
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "HtmlContent",
                  "props": {
                    "content": "{{post?.data?.parent?.content ?? ''}}",
                    "isHtml": "{{(post?.data?.parent?.content_mode ?? 'text') === 'html'}}",
                    "className": "{{_local?.parentContentExpanded ? '' : '[&_img]:hidden [&_table]:hidden'}}"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "4줄: 더보기/접기 토글 버튼 (왼쪽 정렬, 화살표 아이콘) - 200자 이상이고 블라인드 아닌 경우만 표시",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "if": "{{post?.data?.parent?.status !== 'blinded' && (post?.data?.parent?.content ?? '').length > 200}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "flex justify-start"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Button",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:text-gray-200 bg-transparent border-0 p-0 cursor-pointer flex items-center gap-1"
                  },
                  "actions": [
                    {
                      "type": "click",
                      "handler": "setState",
                      "params": {
                        "target": "local",
                        "parentContentExpanded": "{{!_local?.parentContentExpanded}}"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "Icon",
                      "props": {
                        "name": "{{_local?.parentContentExpanded ? 'chevron-up' : 'chevron-down'}}",
                        "size": "sm"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "text": "{{_local?.parentContentExpanded ? '$t:board.show_less' : '$t:board.show_more'}}"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "게시글 내용 영역",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": {
            "className": "p-6"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "comment": "블라인드 처리된 게시글 - 상세 사유 표시",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "if": "{{post?.data?.status === 'blinded'}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "text-center py-12 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900/30 rounded-lg border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "comment": "블라인드 사유 - trigger_type에 따라 동적 표시",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "P",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "Icon",
                      "props": {
                        "name": "eye-slash",
                        "size": "2x"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "P",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2"
                      },
                      "text": "$t:board.blinded_post"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "P",
                  "if": "{{post?.data?.trigger_type}}",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 font-medium"
                  },
                  "text": "$t:board.blinded_reason.{{post?.data?.trigger_type}}"
                },
                {
                  "comment": "원글 보기/숨기기 토글 버튼",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Button",
                  "if": "{{post?.data?.content}}",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "mt-4 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-300 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 mx-auto cursor-pointer"
                  },
                  "actions": [
                    {
                      "type": "click",
                      "handler": "setState",
                      "params": {
                        "target": "local",
                        "showBlindedPostContent": "{{!_local?.showBlindedPostContent}}"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "Icon",
                      "props": {
                        "name": "{{_local?.showBlindedPostContent ? 'eye-slash' : 'eye'}}",
                        "size": "sm"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "text": "{{_local?.showBlindedPostContent ? '$t:board.hide_original' : '$t:board.view_original'}}"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "블라인드 게시글 원본 내용 표시",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "if": "{{post?.data?.status === 'blinded' && _local?.showBlindedPostContent && post?.data?.content}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "mt-4 p-4 bg-base-100 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "flex items-center gap-2 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "Icon",
                      "props": {
                        "name": "file-lines",
                        "size": "sm",
                        "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                      },
                      "text": "$t:board.original_content"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "HtmlContent",
                  "props": {
                    "content": "{{post?.data?.content ?? ''}}",
                    "isHtml": "{{(post?.data?.content_mode ?? 'text') === 'html'}}",
                    "className": "prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "회원 비밀글 - 비로그인 시 로그인 안내",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "if": "{{post?.data?.content === null && !post?.data?.is_guest_post && !_global.currentUser?.uuid && post?.data?.status !== 'blinded'}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "text-center py-12"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "lock",
                    "size": "3x",
                    "className": "mx-auto text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-4"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "P",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6"
                  },
                  "text": "$t:board.secret_post_login_required"
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Button",
                  "props": {
                    "type": "button",
                    "className": "px-6 py-2 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-gray-900 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 dark:hover:bg-gray-100 cursor-pointer"
                  },
                  "text": "$t:common.login",
                  "actions": [
                    {
                      "type": "click",
                      "handler": "navigate",
                      "params": {
                        "path": "/login",
                        "query": {
                          "redirect": "{{_global.currentPath}}"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "회원 비밀글 - 로그인했으나 권한 없음",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "if": "{{post?.data?.content === null && !post?.data?.is_guest_post && _global.currentUser?.uuid && post?.data?.status !== 'blinded'}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "text-center py-12"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "lock",
                    "size": "3x",
                    "className": "mx-auto text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-4"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "P",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"
                  },
                  "text": "$t:board.secret_post_no_permission"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "비회원 비밀글 - 비밀번호 입력 필요",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "if": "{{post?.data?.content === null && post?.data?.is_guest_post && post?.data?.status !== 'blinded'}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "text-center py-12"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "lock",
                    "size": "3x",
                    "className": "mx-auto text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-4"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "P",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6"
                  },
                  "text": "$t:board.secret_post_locked"
                },
                {
                  "comment": "비밀번호 입력 폼",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Form",
                  "dataKey": "secretPasswordForm",
                  "props": {
                    "id": "secretPasswordForm",
                    "className": "max-w-md mx-auto"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Div",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "flex gap-2"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Input",
                          "props": {
                            "type": "password",
                            "name": "password",
                            "placeholder": "$t:board.form.password_placeholder",
                            "className": "flex-1 px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent",
                            "value": "{{_local.secretPasswordForm?.password ?? ''}}"
                          },
                          "actions": [
                            {
                              "type": "change",
                              "handler": "setState",
                              "params": {
                                "target": "local",
                                "secretPasswordForm": {
                                  "password": "{{$event.target.value}}"
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Button",
                          "props": {
                            "type": "submit",
                            "className": "px-6 py-2 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-gray-900 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 dark:hover:bg-gray-100 cursor-pointer disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed",
                            "disabled": "{{_local?.isVerifyingPassword}}"
                          },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "basic",
                              "name": "Icon",
                              "if": "{{_local?.isVerifyingPassword}}",
                              "props": {
                                "name": "spinner",
                                "size": "sm",
                                "className": "animate-spin mr-2"
                              }
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "basic",
                              "name": "Span",
                              "text": "{{_local?.isVerifyingPassword ? '$t:common.confirming' : '$t:common.confirm'}}"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "actions": [
                    {
                      "type": "submit",
                      "handler": "setState",
                      "params": {
                        "target": "local",
                        "isVerifyingPassword": true
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "submit",
                      "handler": "apiCall",
                      "target": "/api/modules/sirsoft-board/boards/{{route.slug}}/posts/{{route.id}}/verify-password",
                      "auth_mode": "optional",
                      "params": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "body": "{{_local?.secretPasswordForm}}"
                      },
                      "onSuccess": [
                        {
                          "handler": "updateDataSource",
                          "params": {
                            "dataSourceId": "post",
                            "data": "{{result}}"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "handler": "setState",
                          "params": {
                            "target": "local",
                            "isVerifyingPassword": false
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "handler": "toast",
                          "params": {
                            "type": "success",
                            "message": "$t:board.password_verified"
                          }
                        }
                      ],
                      "onError": [
                        {
                          "handler": "setState",
                          "params": {
                            "target": "local",
                            "isVerifyingPassword": false,
                            "secretPasswordForm": {
                              "password": ""
                            }
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "handler": "toast",
                          "params": {
                            "type": "error",
                            "message": "{{error.message}}"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "게시글 내용 (정상)",
              "type": "composite",
              "name": "HtmlContent",
              "if": "{{post?.data?.status !== 'blinded' && post?.data?.content !== null}}",
              "props": {
                "content": "{{post?.data?.content ?? ''}}",
                "isHtml": "{{(post?.data?.content_mode ?? 'text') === 'html'}}",
                "className": "prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none mb-6"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "게시글 액션 버튼 영역 (답변, 신고, 수정, 삭제) - 비회원 글은 항상 표시 (수정/삭제용)",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{post?.data?.is_guest_post || post?.data?.is_author || post?.data?.abilities?.can_manage || post?.data?.board?.use_reply || (_global.currentUser?.uuid && post?.data?.board?.use_report)}}",
          "props": {
            "className": "flex justify-end gap-2 px-6 py-4 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "comment": "답변 버튼 (답변 기능 활성화 + depth 제한 + 블라인드 아닌 게시글 + 비밀글은 검증 후)",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "if": "{{post?.data?.board?.use_reply && !post?.data?.is_notice && (post?.data?.depth ?? 0) < (post?.data?.board?.max_reply_depth ?? 1) && post?.data?.abilities?.can_write && post?.data?.status !== 'blinded' && (!post?.data?.is_secret || post?.data?.content !== null)}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "px-4 py-2 text-sm border border-blue-300 dark:border-blue-600 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/20 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 cursor-pointer"
              },
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "click",
                  "handler": "navigate",
                  "params": {
                    "path": "/board/{{route.slug}}/write?parent_id={{route.id}}"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "reply",
                    "size": "sm"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "text": "$t:board.post.reply"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "신고 버튼 — 미신고 상태 (모달 오픈)",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "if": "{{_global.currentUser?.uuid && post?.data?.board?.use_report && !post?.data?.is_author && post?.data?.status !== 'blinded' && (!post?.data?.is_secret || post?.data?.content !== null) && !post?.data?.is_already_reported}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "px-4 py-2 text-sm border border-orange-300 dark:border-orange-600 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-50 dark:hover:bg-orange-900/20 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 cursor-pointer"
              },
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "click",
                  "handler": "sequence",
                  "actions": [
                    {
                      "comment": "공용 신고 모달 설정",
                      "handler": "setState",
                      "params": {
                        "target": "global",
                        "reportModal": {
                          "type": "post",
                          "apiEndpoint": "/api/modules/sirsoft-board/boards/{{route?.slug}}/posts/{{route?.id}}/reports"
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "모달은 modals 섹션이므로 _global로 초기화",
                      "handler": "setState",
                      "params": {
                        "target": "global",
                        "reportForm": {
                          "reason_type": "",
                          "reason_detail": ""
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "handler": "openModal",
                      "target": "board_report_modal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "flag",
                    "size": "sm"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "text": "$t:board.post.report"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "신고 버튼 — 이미 신고한 상태 (클릭 불가)",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "if": "{{_global.currentUser?.uuid && post?.data?.board?.use_report && !post?.data?.is_author && post?.data?.status !== 'blinded' && (!post?.data?.is_secret || post?.data?.content !== null) && post?.data?.is_already_reported}}",
              "props": {
                "disabled": true,
                "className": "px-4 py-2 text-sm border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 rounded-lg flex items-center gap-1 cursor-not-allowed opacity-60"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "flag",
                    "size": "sm"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "text": "$t:board.post.reported"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "수정 버튼 ((회원 권한 && 본인 글) || 비회원 글 || manager 권한) && 삭제되지 않은 글",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "if": "{{!post?.data?.deleted_at && ((post?.data?.is_author && post?.data?.abilities?.can_write) || post?.data?.is_guest_post || post?.data?.abilities?.can_manage)}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "px-4 py-2 text-sm border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 cursor-pointer"
              },
              "actions": [
                {
                  "comment": "비회원/회원 모두 form.json에서 비밀번호 검증 처리",
                  "type": "click",
                  "handler": "navigate",
                  "params": {
                    "path": "/board/{{route.slug}}/{{route.id}}/edit"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "pencil",
                    "size": "sm"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "text": "$t:common.edit"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "삭제 버튼 ((회원 권한 && 본인 글) || 비회원 글 || manager 권한) && 삭제되지 않은 글",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "if": "{{!post?.data?.deleted_at && ((post?.data?.is_author && post?.data?.abilities?.can_write) || post?.data?.is_guest_post || post?.data?.abilities?.can_manage)}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "px-4 py-2 text-sm border border-red-300 dark:border-red-600 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-50 dark:hover:bg-red-900/20 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 cursor-pointer"
              },
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "click",
                  "handler": "sequence",
                  "actions": [
                    {
                      "comment": "공용 삭제 모달 설정 (비회원 본인 글은 isGuest=true, manager 권한이 있으면 비밀번호 불필요)",
                      "handler": "setState",
                      "params": {
                        "target": "global",
                        "deleteModal": {
                          "type": "post",
                          "isGuest": "{{post?.data?.is_guest_post && !post?.data?.abilities?.can_manage}}",
                          "password": "",
                          "apiEndpoint": "/api/modules/sirsoft-board/boards/{{route?.slug}}/posts/{{route?.id}}"
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "handler": "openModal",
                      "target": "board_delete_modal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "trash",
                    "size": "sm"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "text": "$t:common.delete"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "댓글 조회 권한 없음 안내 (댓글 기능 활성화 + 조회 권한 X)",
      "if": "{{post?.data?.board?.use_comment && !post?.data?.abilities?.can_read_comments && (!post?.data?.is_secret || post?.data?.content !== null)}}",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "mt-6 card bg-base-100 shadow-sm"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": {
            "className": "px-6 py-8 text-center"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "composite",
              "name": "Icon",
              "props": {
                "name": "lock",
                "size": "xl",
                "className": "mx-auto text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-600 mb-3"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "P",
              "props": {
                "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
              },
              "text": "$t:board.no_comment_read_permission"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "댓글 섹션 (댓글 기능 활성화 + 댓글 조회 권한) - 비밀글 미검증 시 숨김",
      "if": "{{post?.data?.board?.use_comment && post?.data?.abilities?.can_read_comments && (!post?.data?.is_secret || post?.data?.content !== null)}}",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "mt-6"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "partial": "partials/board/show/_comment_section.json"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "답글 섹션 (답변 기능 활성화 + 답글이 있는 경우) - 비밀글 미검증 시 숨김",
      "if": "{{(post?.data?.replies ?? []).length > 0 && (!post?.data?.is_secret || post?.data?.content !== null)}}",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "mt-6"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "partial": "partials/board/show/_reply_section.json"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
